actually pointless.

50:08.606 --> 50:14.712 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But she added, "I realized
something important,
that science is about discovery,
not just

50:14.745 --> 50:17.248 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
about solving human problems."

50:17.281 --> 50:22.853 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She then spoke a phrase that has
