me over the years. She said, "I
want what

50:22.887 --> 50:25.890 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
you have for my country."

50:25.923 --> 50:30.628 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In her country, Nigeria, there
was simply
no infrastructure for this type
of discovery-based

50:30.661 --> 50:37.001 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
research. In fact, many
solutions to humans'
problems began in a scientist's
laboratory.

50:37.034 --> 50:41.739 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Did you know that some of the
most significant
medical breakthroughs for the
human brain

50:41.772 --> 50:45.276 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
began with research on sea
slugs?

50:45.309 --> 50:50.648 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The value of my work came under
attack again
when Republican Senator Jeff
Flake featured

50:50.681 --> 50:55.753 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
