that highlights what some in
Congress see

50:55.786 --> 51:01.992 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
as wasteful government spending.
They ridiculed
a research project in my lab
that showed how

51:02.026 --> 51:07.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
